Enter the world of sorcery with the Satoru Gojo live wallpaper, featuring his unmatched power and cool demeanor on your Chrome new tab.

The Satoru Gojo Live Wallpaper captures the essence of Gojo’s formidable strength and effortless style. His striking presence, set against a sleek backdrop, brings an air of mystery and excitement to your browsing experience. With every new tab, you'll be reminded of Gojo’s confident and fearless approach to the world.

Features:

Satoru Gojo Live Wallpaper
Google search bar
Addable and removable shortcuts
Date and time display

This Chrome extension offers a visually stunning chrome wallpaper that perfectly complements its practical features. With one of the best chrome live wallpapers out there, your browsing will be both stylish and efficient. Upgrade your chrome background and experience the world of Satoru Gojo every time you open a new tab.
